 />\n<br />\n請轉告該職員及其上司，勿因表達個人意見而受不必要的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n香港人有言論自由。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cb72e9f1df5b24154fc4c6691e3911438c46cd9","tid":1383112,"uid":47226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ba4fab210fea6de2a4375501e0d9ea95a560fa9","tid":1383112,"uid":47226,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"tellme@1823.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n勞工處二級助理勞工事務主任顏武周及運輸事務主任張家寶充分發揮公務員一直以服務香港市民為本，作為市民和政府溝通的橋樑，維護香港核心價值、以港人福祉為核心使命的精神，值得讚揚！<br />\n<br />\n請轉告該職員及其上司，勿因表達個人意見而受不必要的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n香港人有言論自由。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"寫還寫唔該係咁二都改吓唔好個個一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9322fa878656c62c303fe2c1e6492f86146c49d","tid":1383112,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c2480d98dce469955c99b68c087207e617abaa46","tid":1383112,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"推啦 屌"},{"pid":"5e4d9600bda2213af07cb915a4a369b72505e93e","tid":1383112,"uid":259952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"eb17b5a45eb2808052f98d6fcc4481365caa429d","tid":1383112,"uid":112232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:08:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e73c8e2dae401edd8878d61b22983942cd41f0e","tid":1383112,"uid":155339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"已send 推"},{"pid":"d2c6423f8efb132639ce167b578b581c65409ed6","tid":1383112,"uid":283846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78ea30f5496557b8705ddb10938a15b8a6b894f0","tid":1383112,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb72e9f1df5b24154fc4c6691e3911438c46cd9","tid":1383112,"uid":47226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2